    <item>
      <title>英国通胀放缓后，交易员加大对英国央行降息的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/pound-falls-as-uk-inflation-slowdown-opens-door-for-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示英国12月份通胀率意外下降，缓解了人们对持续价格压力的担忧，货币市场纷纷预期英国央行今年将进一步降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/pound-falls-as-uk-inflation-slowdown-opens-door-for-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 07:21:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SGS 与必维国际检验集团商谈 330 亿美元合并计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/sgs-bureau-veritas-to-create-33-billion-european-testing-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SGS SA 正在与 Bureau Veritas SA 洽谈合并，合并后的公司将创建一家欧洲检测和认证公司，合并后市值将超过 330 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/sgs-bureau-veritas-to-create-33-billion-european-testing-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 06:19:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>面对交易员削减押注，欧洲央行仍捍卫降息路径</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/ecb-defends-rate-cutting-path-in-face-of-traders-paring-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行正在反驳那些认为通胀走强、美国就业市场意外强劲以及唐纳德·特朗普的经济混乱将缩小降息空间的投资者的观点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/ecb-defends-rate-cutting-path-in-face-of-traders-paring-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
